rows.label: tlk42200121_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Being able to cook is a kind of
status symbol, mo! People who can
cook should cook more and more, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But in the beginning, everyone has
a small cooking repertoire, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But if you get a new recipe,
your cooking horizons will
expand even more, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_02_msg0004
rows.name:
A meal made with love enriches the
heart, strengthens the body, and
brings a smile to your face, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Let's cook lots of food
in the kitchen, mo!
